--------------------------------------------------------------
			Dependencies
--------------------------------------------------------------
Python: 3.7.4
OpenCV: 4.4.0
Imutils: 0.5.3
Numpy: 1.19.1

to run you must have python 3.7 or greater installed on your
computer.

to check if you have it installed open up a cmd prompt and 
type

python -V or python --version
if this doesnt work

type:

where python, this should return your full path for python.exe

next check to see if pip is installed with the same commands
pip -V or pip --version

once both are installed you can use the following commands
to install the dependencies

depending on which version is downloaded

pip install requirements.txt
pip3 install requirements.txt
-------------------------------------------------------------
			Running
-------------------------------------------------------------
To run the program you will issue the following commands

python3 browser.py [-h] [-r] [-c] [filepath to images]
-h: will bring up a help menu
-r: change the size of rows (default: 720)
-c: change the size of columns (default: 1080)
filepath: will require full file path

